{
  "name": "Peanut Butter Cheesecake Swirl Brownies",
  "description": "Instagram import (reel DZ5M8gatrJw): a fudgy banana-based protein brownie layer under a blended cottage-cheese cheesecake layer with peanut-butter pockets swirled in. A brownie+cheesecake HYBRID like our Salted Caramel Cheesecake Brownie Bars, but the brownie is banana/cocoa/protein (no butter, no flour) instead of butter-fudge. Modeled faithfully as written (medium egg = 44 g per house rule); honey kept as written - house-lean swaps (honey->Splenda, peanut butter->PB powder) noted for tuning.",
